{"id":23,"category_slug":"short-stories","category_name":"Short Stories","position":15,"title":"15. Halloween Night","subtitle":"","level":"A1","parts":29,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/short-stories/15-halloween-night.23/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/15-halloween-night-2019-03-20-04-55-19/0-15-halloween-night.mp3","transcript":"Halloween is fun.\nMy mom buys candy.\nMy mom buys potato chips.\nMy mom buys chocolate bars.\nIt is for the trick-or-treaters.\nMy mom buys me a costume.\nIt is a ghost costume.\nI am going to be scary.\nMy sister is going to dress up as a princess.\nShe will have a wand.\nShe will have a crown.\nShe will look beautiful.\nMy dad buys a pumpkin.\nIt is going to be a Jack O'Lantern.\nWe draw a face on the pumpkin.\nWe carve the face with a knife.\nOur Jack O'Lantern looks funny.\nWe go trick-or-treating.\nWe knock on the neighbor's door.\nWe say, \"trick or treat\".\nOur neighbors give us candy.\nWe say \"Thanks\".\nWe go to many houses.\nWe go home.\nOur parents check our candy.\nIt's safe.\nWe eat lots of candy.\nWe don't feel very good.\nWe go to bed.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:55:30","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Halloween is fun.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/15-halloween-night-2019-03-20-04-55-19/1.mp3","time_start":3.0,"time_end":4.75},{"position":2,"content":"My mom buys candy.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/15-halloween-night-2019-03-20-04-55-19/2.mp3","time_start":5.3,"time_end":7.01},{"position":3,"content":"My mom buys potato chips.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/15-halloween-night-2019-03-20-04-55-19/3.mp3","time_start":7.5,"time_end":9.62},{"position":4,"content":"My mom buys chocolate bars.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/15-halloween-night-2019-03-20-04-55-19/4.mp3","time_start":10.2,"time_end":1